{"tid":253220,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃元山倡維港以外填海應付土地需要","createTime":"2017-05-22T08:27:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-22T13:01:05.000Z","uid":21161,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b51683d9972936c44efb723b1bb02607a88e6cfe","tid":253220,"uid":21161,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T08:27:49.000Z","msg":"團結香港基金副總幹事兼政策研究院主管黃元山表示，每次涉及收回私人業權的過程都很困難，<span style=\"color: red;\">他認同要繼續收回棕地，但收回所有棕地都只得1200公頃，未足以應付香港需要有如3個沙田面積，即是大約9000公頃土地。</span><br />\n<br />\n黃元山在電台節目表示，政府現時的規劃，<span style=\"color: red;\">包括東大嶼都會在內，只有約5000公頃，建議當局需要作大規劃在維港以外的填海方案。</span><br />\n<br />\n香港大學經濟學講座教授王于漸在同一節目表示，樓價租金在過去20年不斷上升，<span style=\"color: red;\">認為當局政策要有大改變，包括公屋及綠置居可租可買等。</span>"},{"pid":"dc5b304b9ea2ae10c3027b35ee58f2212b77e9d7","tid":253220,"uid":21161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T08:28:40.000Z","msg":"3個沙田面積<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ca9be977a87f1d5c2637a61f2a300fabb5ef2ab","tid":253220,"uid":21161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T08:32:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d0a0a85df0da444dcd9b664fc53aaa2b68055050","tid":253220,"uid":21161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T08:35:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a882c427051c4393d3dc889f71d4f20d8848c9f","tid":253220,"uid":21161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T08:39:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ffb5d507ba0b5d0445759ea6273943f58072aa8","tid":253220,"uid":35870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T08:41:39.000Z","msg":"一早就應該填啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd91c32d7be8121415820c06ae0fbe3363d1a29d","tid":253220,"uid":42820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T08:42:45.000Z","msg":"叫支那割D地比香港最合乎經濟原則"},{"pid":"4f529952bedc3e8624fe106056e745039e675ef1","tid":253220,"uid":23993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T08:44:10.000Z","msg":"幾時填平成個維港起豪宅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a29212b869b4c7a8d58a2feab6830edb23663213","tid":253220,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T08:44:58.000Z","msg":"5000 + 1200 = 6200<br />\n<br />\n即係只要多 2800 公頃<br />\n<br />\n之前咪話起人工島<br />\n<br />\n咁都夠哂啦"},{"pid":"fec31939e617e334605229a8c7deaf2089ba80eb","tid":253220,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T08:45:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>3個沙田面積<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啟德果度都大過沙田啦"},{"pid":"da9c2b7dba0eabe988c8fde0e390c513b021de3f","tid":253220,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T08:49:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"17ce485287c87a4fb15f659d8263eb813a9fe238","tid":253220,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T08:53:31.000Z","msg":"要9000公頃土地的理由?<br />\n因為要俾每日150隻蝗住??<br />\n點解唔cut quota??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbbef6a0c300d8094073230e841fc4fc790c3bcd","tid":253220,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T08:54:49.000Z","msg":"源頭減廢"},{"pid":"6c178bfa292754b8e0c49314feae7a1b7456e48d","tid":253220,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T09:02:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n黃元山.......於<strong>1997至2004年間任職雷曼兄弟（Lehman Brothers）衍生工具部</strong>，長駐紐約及倫敦；其後轉至瑞士銀行（UBS）倫敦任執行董事（Executive Director）。然後<strong>2005年轉至英國蘇格蘭皇家銀行（RBS）工作，擔任亞洲區董事總經理暨債券部管理委員會委員，負責主管亞太區結構信貸衍生部門。</strong><br />\n<br />\n黃元山先後在雷曼兄弟的紐約總部和倫敦分行工作，<strong>前後7年，2004年離職時已晉升至副總裁。他有份參與設計雷曼兄弟的第一代抵押債務證券產品</strong>。 [5]<br />\n由2015年11月1日起，黃元山獲團結香港基金會委任為副總幹事兼公共政策部主管。[6]....<br />\n<br />\n自己係有份搞次按既仆街, <br />\n出左事冇得撈, 就出幾本唔知點解同trader, guns and money咁上下內容既書扮正義扮智者,<br />\n然後就奶共揾著數<br />\n<br />\n你做仆街就算啦, 做完仲要成日上電台鳩吹扮正義, 好撚嘔心呀"},{"pid":"fc59341aa8197c89a70b375eee32d350f1fafca9","tid":253220,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T09:05:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d08e540e87630bf80ae23f4074fc2e8f2b05e44b","tid":253220,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T09:07:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n黃元山.......於<strong>1997至2004年間任職雷曼兄弟（Lehman Brothers）衍生工具部</strong>，長駐紐約及倫敦；其後轉至瑞士銀行（UBS）倫敦任執行董事（Executive Director）。然後<strong>2005年轉至英國蘇格蘭皇家銀行（RBS）工作，擔任亞洲區董事總經理暨債券部管理委員會委員，負責主管亞太區結構信貸衍生部門。</strong><br />\n<br />\n黃元山先後在雷曼兄弟的紐約總部和倫敦分行工作，<strong>前後7年，2004年離職時已晉升至副總裁。他有份參與設計雷曼兄弟的第一代抵押債務證券產品</strong>。 [5]<br />\n由2015年11月1日起，黃元山獲團結香港基金會委任為副總幹事兼公共政策部主管。[6]....<br />\n<br />\n自己係有份搞次按既仆街, <br />\n出左事冇得撈, 就出幾本唔知點解同trader, guns and money咁上下內容既書扮正義扮智者,<br />\n然後就奶共揾著數<br />\n<br />\n你做仆街就算啦, 做完仲要成日上電台鳩吹扮正義, 好撚嘔心呀</blockquote><br />\n其實黃元山一向都廢廢地冇咩料到<br />\n講公共政策成日錯</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其他算<br />\n見到佢早幾年屌投行太貪心乜乜柒柒就覺好嘔心<br />\n屌你你自己有份架"},{"pid":"5076bc9a0d414b869e4a07c0e6a9c609c51980fd","tid":253220,"uid":21161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T09:09:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>填船灣淡水湖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實剷一半大嶼山已經好ok"},{"pid":"c0dff1b544f0ea008f5f61456f85c9fdd3f990f0","tid":253220,"uid":33787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T09:10:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pi